She sees Scorponok take off. SHe opened her link,"Hey Stringtra, 
disreguard what I said earlier about help.  Scorponok went after the 
mouse. NOW I could use some help.  Send Rowdy if you can find him."

She fired a few more rounds off,"And tell him not to dwaddle about. I 
could really use the help this time." as she fired again.
